metadata.name: Lucy Lucky - Rabbit a symbol of grace & beauty
metadata.description:
A symbol of grace and beauty, with her sleek metallic exterior embodying the elegance of the rabbit. Her mechanical enhancements only add to her natural charm, representing the advancement of technology and the limitless potential of the future. The delicate curve of her frame represents the softness and compassion, known for their calming and peaceful nature. She stands tall and proud, radiating a sense of mercy and kindness, reminding us all to cherish the beauty of life in every form.

3508 x 4961
